1
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:38,780
Mast! Lay down the mast!

2
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:46,340
Hurry up and get the rope!

3
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:50,340
Bow and stern face the banks! Quick!

4
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:56,420
Thousands of homes are brightly lit,

5
00:00:56,420 --> 00:00:58,860
and the doors to them are wide open.

6
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:01,020
This is East Capital.

7
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:04,620
New wine from Sunyang Restaurant!

8
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:07,140
Welcome to enjoy it!

9
00:01:07,300 --> 00:01:09,820
​If you want to know what happens next,

10
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:11,900
wait until next time.

11
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:14,420
People from all over the world gather here,

12
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:17,380
and envoys from various countries come to communicate with the authorities.

13
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,660
[Riverside Code at Qingming Festival]

14
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,660
[Adapted from Ye Wenbiao's Novel Series of the Same Name]

15
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:27,980
[Episode 24]

16
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:29,120
[With a steadfast heart comes fulfillment. Fulfillment keeps troubles out,]

17
00:01:29,140 --> 00:01:29,980
[and peace follows. - Zhang Zai, Northern Song Dynasty]

18
00:01:30,270 --> 00:01:30,800
Yue,

19
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:33,480
are you blaming me for being ruthless?

20
00:01:39,910 --> 00:01:41,310
But everything I've painstakingly done

21
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,800
has been to clear the Su family's name

22
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,870
and to seek justice for our parents, who died unjustly.

23
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,480
Yue,

24
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,190
if you think I'm wrong,

25
00:01:52,630 --> 00:01:54,000
kill me now.

26
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:58,830
Su Zheng,

27
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:04,870
if you truly are from the Su family,

28
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,360
if you really are my younger brother,

29
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,080
then I ask you to stop.

30
00:02:48,110 --> 00:02:49,630
Beautiful umbrellas for sale!

31
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:51,080
Darling, this is the place.

32
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,030
Wen's Umbrella Shop.

33
00:02:52,270 --> 00:02:53,080
[Wen's Umbrellas for Rain and Sun]
This one?

34
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,240
Why is it closed?

35
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,390
That's odd.

36
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,160
It should be open at this hour.

37
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,550
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]
Why don't we come back tomorrow?

38
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:00,630
Just...

39
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:01,520
Excuse me.

40
00:03:01,670 --> 00:03:03,110
Are you shopping for umbrellas?

41
00:03:03,390 --> 00:03:03,880
Yes.

42
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,600
- We'd like to place a large order. - That's right.

43
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,240
That's great.

44
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,390
Take a look at my umbrellas.

45
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,720
They're just

46
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:10,550
as good as hers.

47
00:03:11,390 --> 00:03:12,470
I'll even give you a discount.

48
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,390
Listen,

49
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,830
Manager Wen

50
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:16,910
won't be back anytime soon.

51
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:18,160
If you place your order here,

52
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,320
you'll definitely face delays.

53
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:22,030
Manager Liu, watch your words.

54
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:25,110
All the regulars know she never delays orders.

55
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:26,520
She just closed early because she had to

56
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,720
take care of some family matters.

57
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,830
On the other hand, you seem

58
00:03:29,270 --> 00:03:30,390
to be quite idle.

59
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,000
You've been out of business for a month, haven't you?

60
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:32,830
You...

61
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,830
Watch your tone.

62
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,000
You...!

63
00:03:36,390 --> 00:03:36,960
She's back.

64
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,470
Just you wait!

65
00:03:41,550 --> 00:03:42,880
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]
Go on. Take a look at her umbrellas.

66
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,440
All right.

67
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,320
Are you two quarreling again?

68
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:52,110
Let me remind you. Many women have their eyes

69
00:03:52,110 --> 00:03:53,360
on your husband.

70
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,830
If you're not careful,

71
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:55,960
your perfect husband

72
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,160
might end up like these customers,

73
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,240
stolen by someone else.

74
00:03:59,160 --> 00:03:59,880
Thanks.

75
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:04,260
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]

76
00:04:04,470 --> 00:04:05,880
Freshly steamed bao!

77
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,750
Interrogate the Luan couple immediately.

78
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:08,910
Where's Inspector Gu?

79
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,910
- Where's Inspector Gu? - Judge Wan.

80
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,550
Boss,

81
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:12,160
Boss,

82
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:14,240
some men from the Ministry of Justice showed up with an insignia

83
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,830
and took the Luan couple away.

84
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:18,070
But they didn't take them to the Ministry of Justice.

85
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,880
Stupid wretch!

86
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:32,270
"The river grows cold

87
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,880
as sunlight fades from the tower"?

88
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,830
Did you sing

89
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,600
those unlucky lyrics to mock me?

90
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:42,350
You cheap servant!

91
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,110
Ziyin,

92
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,110
don't be upset.

93
00:04:46,670 --> 00:04:48,070
This wretch must be punished

94
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:48,920
for angering you.

95
00:04:49,110 --> 00:04:49,790
Now hurry,

96
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,670
apologize with a drink

97
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,880
and sing another song!

98
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:53,670
All right, calm down.

99
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,790
Put your hands down.

100
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,550
Apologize

101
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,550
with a drink? No way.

102
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,390
Lift your head.

103
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:25,670
Don't think I'll let you off

104
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,480
with just a simple toast.

105
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:37,670
Enough, Ziyin.

106
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,160
Give it to me.

107
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,950
Ziyin,

108
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:43,160
why let a wretch spoil your mood?

109
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,110
Here, sir.

110
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,320
Feeling better now?

111
00:06:02,550 --> 00:06:04,320
If you'd been here any later,

112
00:06:04,670 --> 00:06:06,390
even an ant would have dared

113
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:08,350
to humiliate me, let alone these servants.

114
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:15,390
Ziyin, are you holding a grudge against me?

115
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,920
When I was young,

116
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,550
I devoted myself entirely to officialdom

117
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,550
to restore the glory of the Zou family.

118
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:30,510
I wasn't able to spend much time with you.

119
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:32,070
So I thought

120
00:06:33,350 --> 00:06:35,200
I should at least choose

121
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:37,350
a suitable husband for you

122
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:42,550
to make up for my failings as a father.

123
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:52,940
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]

124
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,510
Yue.

125
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:06,320
I was wrong.

126
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,670
Please don't be angry with me.

127
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,720
Were you really wrong?

128
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,070
You weren't.

129
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,200
There's nothing wrong with wanting to avenge our parents.

130
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,920
So, Yue, you're willing to join me in seeking revenge?

131
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,720
There are things in this world

132
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,830
that are far more important than revenge.

133
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,950
Mother!

134
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,270
Run!

135
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,440
Don't look back.

136
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:38,480
"Don't look back."

137
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:41,830
Those were Mother's

138
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,110
last words to me before she died.

139
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,510
I'm grateful to her

140
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:48,790
for giving me the strength to survive.

141
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,670
Right or wrong,

142
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,070
good or bad,

143
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:56,350
I've lived.

144
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,040
I've had a life.

145
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:01,000
Humble and ordinary

146
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,000
as it's been,

147
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,230
it's had many happy moments,

148
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,200
and that's enough.

149
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,830
But with Zou Mian still alive,

150
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,640
how can you truly be happy?

151
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,830
How can we just watch the man

152
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:16,920
who killed our parents walk free before our eyes

153
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,230
and do nothing?

154
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:19,920
How can we live with that?

155
00:08:20,390 --> 00:08:21,110
Zheng,

156
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,040
I hope you can

157
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,550
find and live your own life.

158
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,480
What do you mean, Yue?

159
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,230
Live.

160
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:37,790
And live well.

161
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,000
Come to think of it, Father,

162
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:49,910
you've put me through so much.

163
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:51,790
Ziyin,

164
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,880
don't be upset.

165
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,230
Hui married into our family,

166
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:00,710
so even after I got married,

167
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:02,960
I was still able to stay by your side

168
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,080
and serve you as a dutiful daughter.

169
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,350
But you

170
00:09:05,350 --> 00:09:07,000
had to get him a job

171
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:08,640
here in the East Capital,

172
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:12,110
leaving me separated from you all these years.

173
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:15,230
The East Capital is

174
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,030
where people from all over the world gather

175
00:09:18,710 --> 00:09:20,280
and where envoys from various nations come to communicate.

176
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,790
I need someone

177
00:09:22,230 --> 00:09:23,910
to stay here for me.

178
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,030
Who else could I trust

179
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,280
but my own family?

180
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,670
Besides,

181
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,840
with my son-in-law's talents,

182
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:39,030
wouldn't it have been a waste for him to stay in the South?

183
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,440
Thank you for your confidence in me, sir.

184
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:43,470
I'm sorry

185
00:09:43,470 --> 00:09:45,840
for failing you and causing you trouble.

186
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:49,470
Hui is no fool.

187
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:51,710
His arrest

188
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,910
was a setup.

189
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,080
Indeed.

190
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,710
Father,

191
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:01,640
you got us straight out of prison.

192
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:04,110
Does that mean you've taken care of everything for us?

193
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:07,550
To get

194
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:10,280
the two of you out this time,

195
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:15,350
I used every connection I had.

196
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:17,030
This half-day reunion

197
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,960
didn't come easy.

198
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:21,350
Half-day reunion?

199
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:24,790
Does that mean we have to go back

200
00:10:26,110 --> 00:10:27,470
at dawn tomorrow?

201
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,670
I'd rather die

202
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:30,200
than return to that filthy place!

203
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,880
Even if you wanted to go back,

204
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,400
Father wouldn't let you.

205
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,520
Right, Father?

206
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:41,180
Sir,

207
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:42,670
by dawn tomorrow,

208
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:43,140
I'll...

209
00:10:43,140 --> 00:10:43,670
No,

210
00:10:44,110 --> 00:10:44,870
I'll take Ziyin

211
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:47,180
back to the South right now.

212
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,380
We'll live in the countryside.

213
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:49,260
I promise you, sir,

214
00:10:49,260 --> 00:10:51,700
not a word of this will be revealed to anyone.

215
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:54,310
We'll disappear from the world entirely.

216
00:10:54,310 --> 00:10:55,110
Sir,

217
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:58,580
please save me.

218
00:10:58,820 --> 00:11:00,310
What are you doing?

219
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:03,670
It seems your husband

220
00:11:04,470 --> 00:11:06,310
still doesn't know you well enough.

221
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:12,350
You were born into wealth and privilege.

222
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:14,870
How could you possibly live in seclusion in the mountains?

223
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:16,230
Sir...

224
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:19,870
Hui?

225
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:21,380
Hui!

226
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:22,790
Hui!

227
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:23,790
Hui, what...?

228
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:30,230
Father,

229
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:32,470
Hui may have done wrong,

230
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:35,260
but he did it for the sake of our family.

231
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:37,670
He is my husband.

232
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:38,790
Father,

233
00:11:39,110 --> 00:11:40,430
please spare his life.

234
00:11:40,430 --> 00:11:41,740
He is your husband,

235
00:11:41,740 --> 00:11:43,310
but he's also married into the Zou family!

236
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:45,550
The situation has spiraled out of control.

237
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:47,030
The people are outraged,

238
00:11:47,230 --> 00:11:48,500
and the Emperor is furious.

239
00:11:49,110 --> 00:11:50,620
Cutting off an arm to save the body

240
00:11:50,990 --> 00:11:52,430
is the only way to preserve the Zou family.

241
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:57,030
I know everything

242
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:59,580
you two have done

243
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:01,990
in the East Capital

244
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:03,550
over the years.

245
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:08,820
Luan Hui brought about this disaster

246
00:12:10,060 --> 00:12:11,470
by exploiting the Zou family's power

247
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:13,550
to satisfy his greed.

248
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:18,550
Out of familial affection,

249
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:20,740
I pulled some strings

250
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:22,820
to get him released,

251
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:26,580
allowing him to leave with a shred of dignity.

252
00:12:26,580 --> 00:12:29,670
That's already the most I could do for him!

253
00:12:33,110 --> 00:12:34,430
In critical moments,

254
00:12:35,260 --> 00:12:37,060
sacrificing oneself for the greater good

255
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,990
is what true family does.

256
00:12:40,380 --> 00:12:42,430
If I let him live,

257
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:44,470
the entire Zou family

258
00:12:45,140 --> 00:12:47,030
would be dragged down with him.

259
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:50,790
Sir,

260
00:12:51,430 --> 00:12:52,500
sir.

261
00:12:57,620 --> 00:12:58,470
Ziyin,

262
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:00,350
save me.

263
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:03,500
Save me.

264
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:05,430
Hui,

265
00:13:06,350 --> 00:13:07,500
I've been with you for years.

266
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:10,620
Of course, I don't want to lose you.

267
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,740
But for the sake of the Zou family,

268
00:13:14,310 --> 00:13:15,940
even if it breaks my heart,

269
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,870
I have to respect Father's decision.

270
00:13:20,310 --> 00:13:21,110
Don't worry.

271
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:24,030
I'll take care of your family.

272
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:25,620
You can go in peace.

273
00:13:30,430 --> 00:13:31,700
Zou Ziyin,

274
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:36,110
you're so heartless!

275
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:39,110
You're such a venomous snake.

276
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:41,700
I knew

277
00:13:43,230 --> 00:13:44,670
you never truly

278
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:46,110
cared for me.

279
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:49,940
You don't deserve my love for you all these years.

280
00:13:55,380 --> 00:13:56,180
Zou Mian.

281
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:58,060
Zou Mian!

282
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:03,500
I, a man of dignity, married into your family.

283
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:04,670
Do you think

284
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:06,700
I didn't know why you chose me?

285
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:13,550
I swallowed my pride,

286
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:15,230
endured humiliation,

287
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:17,500
and worked like a slave for you.

288
00:14:19,230 --> 00:14:21,110
And this is how you repay me?

289
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:23,060
If I can't

290
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:24,700
live today,

291
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:28,620
you're dying with me!

292
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:35,030
Without my family's support,

293
00:14:35,740 --> 00:14:38,310
you would've been nothing but a poor village tutor!

294
00:14:38,620 --> 00:14:40,550
You'd never have had the chance to even set foot

295
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:42,140
in the East Capital.

296
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:44,310
And now you're trying to kill me?

297
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,310
What a joke!

298
00:14:59,990 --> 00:15:01,350
Why am I...?

299
00:15:04,470 --> 00:15:06,260
Get over yourself.

300
00:15:08,940 --> 00:15:11,820
You're just an abandoned pawn, too.

301
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:19,550
Father,

302
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:21,380
Father!

303
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:24,700
Why?

304
00:15:32,030 --> 00:15:32,910
Father,

305
00:15:34,430 --> 00:15:36,790
I don't want to die.

306
00:16:12,570 --> 00:16:14,690
[Imperial Edict]

307
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:41,140
Boss,

308
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:43,740
what do we do now?

309
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,260
Zou Mian, that old villain,

310
00:16:46,470 --> 00:16:47,820
has come to the East Capital.

311
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:53,230
We can't let him escape.

312
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:56,470
I've waited for this day

313
00:16:58,740 --> 00:17:00,380
for 15 years.

314
00:17:03,300 --> 00:17:06,900
[Kaifeng Court]

315
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:11,460
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]

316
00:17:20,460 --> 00:17:22,070
Why did you close the shop so early?

317
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:23,620
You're here.

318
00:17:26,740 --> 00:17:28,260
This isn't like you,

319
00:17:28,260 --> 00:17:29,310
Manager Wen.

320
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:31,910
It seems your luck's been pretty bad lately.

321
00:17:31,980 --> 00:17:33,710
I know a fortune-teller.

322
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:35,140
Why don't I bring him over for a reading?

323
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:05,830
I'm not stopping because I think you've outdone me.

324
00:18:05,910 --> 00:18:07,500
I just hate seeing you take out your frustration

325
00:18:07,500 --> 00:18:08,100
on the umbrella.

326
00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:10,460
What's going on?

327
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:13,790
Manager Fei,

328
00:18:15,260 --> 00:18:19,260
I don't have friends here in the East Capital.

329
00:18:20,380 --> 00:18:21,550
Come to think of it,

330
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:23,980
you seem to be the only person I can really

331
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:25,590
share my thoughts with.

332
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:29,340
I don't see you as a friend.

333
00:18:29,590 --> 00:18:31,260
I see you as my rival.

334
00:18:32,910 --> 00:18:35,260
Do you think my life is better than yours?

335
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:38,670
Now you're hurting my feelings.

336
00:18:39,030 --> 00:18:40,070
That's not what I meant.

337
00:18:41,380 --> 00:18:42,310
Well,

338
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:44,460
I admit I do envy you.

339
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:46,670
We've known each other for over a decade,

340
00:18:46,860 --> 00:18:48,550
and I've spent just as long competing with you,

341
00:18:49,190 --> 00:18:50,140
over the quality of our umbrellas,

342
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:51,950
the success of our shops,

343
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:53,260
and even the devotion of our men.

344
00:18:54,430 --> 00:18:57,380
At first, I hated myself for it.

345
00:18:58,430 --> 00:19:00,030
But eventually, I figured it out.

346
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:01,460
Life

347
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:02,950
is about living.

348
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:04,190
While we're alive,

349
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:05,590
we should make every day count.

350
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:07,380
Without you as my rival,

351
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,910
I wouldn't have had the motivation.

352
00:19:09,910 --> 00:19:11,100
Then what if someone

353
00:19:11,460 --> 00:19:13,460
tried to take away your good life?

354
00:19:14,190 --> 00:19:15,190
What would you do?

355
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:16,980
I won't let anyone

356
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:19,100
take what's mine.

357
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:20,590
If someone tried to take it,

358
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:22,220
I'd make them regret it.

359
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:24,460
I'd grab a feather duster and chase them out.

360
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,190
That makes sense.

361
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:30,190
Anyway, what's been on your mind?

362
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:32,220
Lately,

363
00:19:32,710 --> 00:19:34,340
I've been caught up in some troubles.

364
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:36,830
But your words

365
00:19:37,380 --> 00:19:39,710
have helped me sort things out.

366
00:19:40,950 --> 00:19:43,380
That's more like the Manager Wen I've been competing with all these years.

367
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:46,220
All right, I'm heading back to my shop.

368
00:19:47,790 --> 00:19:49,220
Oh, I almost forgot.

369
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:50,500
Manager Yu from the tailor's shop

370
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:52,340
asked you to stop by tomorrow evening.

371
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:56,140
Too busy thinking about fortune-telling, huh?

372
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:58,500
Anyway, I'm leaving.

373
00:19:58,980 --> 00:19:59,910
Goodbye, Fei.

374
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:14,550
Master,

375
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:16,260
my condolences.

376
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:20,950
I spoiled her too much,

377
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:25,430
letting her and her husband act recklessly,

378
00:20:25,430 --> 00:20:27,100
They caused public outrage

379
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:28,460
and even

380
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:30,310
lost the ledger,

381
00:20:30,310 --> 00:20:32,030
which led to this disaster.

382
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:33,550
They gave

383
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:36,860
those who covet my position the perfect excuse

384
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:38,860
to attack me.

385
00:20:40,430 --> 00:20:42,830
I can't even protect myself now.

386
00:20:43,220 --> 00:20:44,190
If I'd let them live,

387
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:46,070
I wouldn't be able to escape suspicion

388
00:20:46,340 --> 00:20:48,550
when the investigation points to me.

389
00:20:48,950 --> 00:20:52,460
With the Zou family's future uncertain,

390
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:55,100
perhaps death

391
00:20:56,340 --> 00:20:59,740
was the easier way out for Ziyin.

392
00:21:01,190 --> 00:21:01,950
Master,

393
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:03,950
I'm sure she'd understand

394
00:21:04,790 --> 00:21:07,140
your intentions in the afterlife.

395
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:08,980
Transport Ziyin

396
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:12,740
and her husband back to prison tomorrow.

397
00:21:13,030 --> 00:21:15,380
Make sure the record says they died of illness.

398
00:21:15,790 --> 00:21:16,380
Also,

399
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:19,500
spread the word that I'm hosting a grand banquet tomorrow night

400
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:22,190
on this ship on the outskirts.

401
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:24,500
It will surely draw unwanted guests.

402
00:21:24,620 --> 00:21:26,380
Meanwhile, we'll slip away unnoticed,

403
00:21:26,430 --> 00:21:27,860
like a cicada shedding its shell.

404
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:31,140
My years in the Manufacturing Bureau have taught me

405
00:21:31,140 --> 00:21:32,980
the Emperor's preferences.

406
00:21:33,310 --> 00:21:36,950
If I can present that stone to him,

407
00:21:36,950 --> 00:21:38,980
it will surely delight him,

408
00:21:38,980 --> 00:21:40,590
and all will be well.

409
00:21:40,590 --> 00:21:41,980
After that,

410
00:21:42,950 --> 00:21:45,620
I'll deal with the traitors one by one

411
00:21:45,980 --> 00:21:48,950
and use them to honor my Ziyin.

412
00:21:51,140 --> 00:21:52,380
It's starting!

413
00:21:52,670 --> 00:21:54,070
It's starting. Let's go listen.

414
00:21:55,030 --> 00:21:57,500
They say a rare stone

415
00:21:58,220 --> 00:22:01,220
has been discovered in a lake down south.

416
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:02,950
A rare stone?

417
00:22:03,100 --> 00:22:05,140
This stone is said to have been forged by the heavens.

418
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:06,790
It shines as brightly as the sun and moon,

419
00:22:06,950 --> 00:22:09,430
symbolizing the prosperity of the Great Song.

420
00:22:09,670 --> 00:22:10,220
Amazing!

421
00:22:11,070 --> 00:22:11,620
Wonderful!

422
00:22:11,860 --> 00:22:13,190
The Astronomical Bureau

423
00:22:13,190 --> 00:22:14,910
observes the stars at night

424
00:22:16,190 --> 00:22:17,670
and concludes that if this stone

425
00:22:17,860 --> 00:22:20,100
can be brought to the capital at an auspicious hour,

426
00:22:20,190 --> 00:22:23,310
the Great Song will enjoy eternal prosperity.

427
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:24,590
Really?

428
00:22:24,860 --> 00:22:25,790
On this day,

429
00:22:26,190 --> 00:22:29,260
the Emperor's favored official, Mr. Zou,

430
00:22:30,070 --> 00:22:31,910
is ordered to escort the stone by ship

431
00:22:31,910 --> 00:22:34,860
to present it to His Majesty.

432
00:22:34,950 --> 00:22:38,070
This Mr. Zou is none other

433
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:39,590
than Zou Mian.

434
00:22:41,190 --> 00:22:43,950
His reputation precedes him.

435
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:45,500
Some say

436
00:22:45,710 --> 00:22:50,260
he's been extorting the people's wealth and oppressing the common folk

437
00:22:50,620 --> 00:22:53,070
under the guise of collecting rare treasures

438
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:54,620
for the Emperor.

439
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:58,100
Inspector Gu,

440
00:22:58,500 --> 00:22:58,980
Mr. Zhao,

441
00:22:58,980 --> 00:22:59,860
I'm truly sorry,

442
00:23:00,030 --> 00:23:01,550
but I really didn't notice anyone

443
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:02,670
from the Ministry of Justice

444
00:23:02,670 --> 00:23:04,460
passing by with the Luan couple.

445
00:23:04,670 --> 00:23:05,430
That's all right.

446
00:23:05,710 --> 00:23:07,790
You've already been a great help.

447
00:23:07,790 --> 00:23:09,790
Finding clues in your painting

448
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:10,710
would've been a stroke of luck.

449
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:12,790
Not finding anything is perfectly normal.

450
00:23:13,710 --> 00:23:14,670
Zhen,

451
00:23:14,670 --> 00:23:15,830
let's come up with another plan.

452
00:23:15,950 --> 00:23:16,860
I can help you.

453
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:21,740
Lady Wang.

454
00:23:23,500 --> 00:23:25,710
How did you know we were here?

455
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:28,860
My father left the city last night.

456
00:23:29,190 --> 00:23:30,260
Before he left

457
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:33,430
I overheard him discussing with some elders

458
00:23:33,790 --> 00:23:34,980
about a secret meeting

459
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:37,340
with an esteemed guest on the river tonight.

460
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:38,340
An esteemed guest?

461
00:23:39,220 --> 00:23:40,030
Zou Mian.

462
00:23:40,710 --> 00:23:43,460
My father said they'd be going

463
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:44,910
to a wild forest

464
00:23:44,910 --> 00:23:46,740
by the Bian River in the eastern suburbs.

465
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:53,030
Perhaps...

466
00:23:56,590 --> 00:23:58,620
Lady Wang, thank you so much.

467
00:23:59,380 --> 00:24:00,340
Inspector Gu

468
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:01,740
owes you

469
00:24:02,140 --> 00:24:03,910
a big favor for this.

470
00:24:03,910 --> 00:24:04,710
Right.

471
00:24:04,910 --> 00:24:06,100
How are you ever going to repay her?

472
00:24:06,100 --> 00:24:06,910
Wait, Buyou.

473
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:07,710
Buyou...

474
00:24:10,380 --> 00:24:10,980
Found anything?

475
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:19,590
How do you plan to thank me?

476
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:22,340
- How do you plan to thank me? - Inspector Gu!

477
00:24:22,740 --> 00:24:23,550
This is the place.

478
00:24:32,550 --> 00:24:34,310
Here's to Mr. Zou.

479
00:24:35,220 --> 00:24:36,430
Cheers!

480
00:24:39,340 --> 00:24:40,380
Come on.

481
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:42,340
Let's have another drink to congratulate Mr. Zou!

482
00:24:45,740 --> 00:24:47,860
This rare stone you found is truly something, Mr. Zou.

483
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:48,590
It's an auspicious sign.

484
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:51,460
It must be a heavenly blessing for Mr. Zou!

485
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:52,830
What a blessing for Mr. Zou!

486
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:54,260
You're sure to earn imperial favor!

487
00:24:56,190 --> 00:24:57,710
What a heavenly blessing

488
00:24:57,710 --> 00:24:59,100
for Mr. Zou!

489
00:24:59,500 --> 00:25:00,740
- Yes. - It's all thanks to Mr. Zou.

490
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:05,790
Don't move.

491
00:25:07,430 --> 00:25:08,190
Where are the others?

492
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,340
Please, spare me!

493
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:10,380
It's just

494
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:11,620
the two of us here.

495
00:25:13,380 --> 00:25:14,140
Impossible.

496
00:25:14,310 --> 00:25:15,620
I heard men's voices just now.

497
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:18,430
Thank you for your support, Mr. Zou.

498
00:25:18,740 --> 00:25:19,710
Here's to you, Mr. Zou.

499
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:20,460
Madam,

500
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:22,380
we're shadow play and vocal performers.

501
00:25:22,670 --> 00:25:23,220
Last night,

502
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:25,100
someone paid us

503
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,100
to come here and perform.

504
00:25:26,140 --> 00:25:28,030
They told us to create the illusion that Mr. Zou was here.

505
00:25:28,140 --> 00:25:30,260
It seems they were trying to lure someone in.

506
00:25:30,260 --> 00:25:31,100
Catch the assassin!

507
00:25:31,590 --> 00:25:32,430
Catch the assassin!

508
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:33,140
Hurry!

509
00:25:33,340 --> 00:25:34,030
Follow them!

510
00:25:44,740 --> 00:25:49,860
[Hats and Boots, Trustworthy Service]

511
00:25:49,860 --> 00:25:57,420
[Shop for Sale]

512
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:02,980
Did you ask for me?

513
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:05,100
Wen Yue, you're here.

514
00:26:05,190 --> 00:26:06,590
Are you planning to sell the shop?

515
00:26:07,910 --> 00:26:09,340
I'm getting old.

516
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:10,590
I can't keep this up anymore.

517
00:26:14,340 --> 00:26:15,140
Come warm yourself by the fire.

518
00:26:15,140 --> 00:26:15,860
Come on.

519
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:17,260
Warm up.

520
00:26:29,670 --> 00:26:30,460
There's no one in the cabin.

521
00:26:30,550 --> 00:26:31,310
No one on the deck either.

522
00:26:34,830 --> 00:26:35,860
The boat is empty.

523
00:26:42,190 --> 00:26:44,190
That old fox Zou Mian played us.

524
00:26:47,860 --> 00:26:48,670
Boss,

525
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:51,030
the Luan couple were our key witnesses.

526
00:26:51,220 --> 00:26:52,500
What do we do now?

527
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:53,550
Without their testimony,

528
00:26:53,620 --> 00:26:55,710
we can't link the ledger to Zou Mian.

529
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,500
Forget the evidence.

530
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:00,860
I'll take our men right now

531
00:27:01,430 --> 00:27:03,380
to intercept him and finish him off!

532
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:04,550
Brothers!

533
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,220
Yes, sir!

534
00:27:05,590 --> 00:27:06,220
Follow me!

535
00:27:06,910 --> 00:27:07,860
Wan Fu, wait!

536
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:09,670
With so few men,

537
00:27:09,670 --> 00:27:10,460
you won't stand a chance.

538
00:27:10,740 --> 00:27:12,220
Zou Mian is heavily guarded.

539
00:27:12,220 --> 00:27:13,380
If you go near him now,

540
00:27:13,910 --> 00:27:15,220
it'll be a bloodbath.

541
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:17,340
None of you will come back alive!

542
00:27:17,340 --> 00:27:18,340
I'm not afraid to die.

543
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:19,710
Are you?

544
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:21,030
No!

545
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:24,620
Gu Zhen,

546
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:26,380
say something.

547
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:30,740
Don't forget

548
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:32,550
what Kaifeng Court stands for.

549
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,590
It's a place where every grievance is addressed,

550
00:27:34,670 --> 00:27:36,260
and every crime is investigated.

551
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,460
It's not a place for personal vendettas.

552
00:27:38,860 --> 00:27:40,790
Zou Mian deserves to die,

553
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:42,980
but we should bring him to justice,

554
00:27:43,190 --> 00:27:45,030
expose his crimes to the world,

555
00:27:45,100 --> 00:27:47,190
and let the people of the East Capital see his true nature.

556
00:27:47,710 --> 00:27:49,340
That's what we should be doing.

557
00:27:50,310 --> 00:27:51,100
Brothers,

558
00:27:52,550 --> 00:27:54,310
trust me. Don't go.

559
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:55,830
Inspector Gu,

560
00:27:56,950 --> 00:27:57,910
please,

561
00:27:58,460 --> 00:27:59,220
stop them.

562
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:18,550
Expose his crimes to the world

563
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:21,140
and bring him to justice?

564
00:28:21,190 --> 00:28:21,790
Exactly.

565
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:24,030
I want that, too,

566
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:27,140
but I just can't.

567
00:28:34,860 --> 00:28:35,670
Proceed.

568
00:28:53,030 --> 00:28:53,830
Inspector Gu,

569
00:28:54,340 --> 00:28:55,740
I've got an idea!

570
00:28:58,060 --> 00:29:00,160
[Hats and Boots, Trustworthy Service]

571
00:29:00,190 --> 00:29:02,260
You said you had something to tell me?

572
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:03,620
No rush.

573
00:29:04,430 --> 00:29:06,550
You'll know soon enough.

574
00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:08,620
It's been

575
00:29:08,910 --> 00:29:11,070
15 years already.

576
00:29:11,340 --> 00:29:12,500
I still remember the day

577
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:15,310
you and Buyou first met in my shop.

578
00:29:15,910 --> 00:29:17,190
How did so many people die?

579
00:29:19,620 --> 00:29:20,740
Who pushed me?

580
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:23,590
Something's happened by the river!

581
00:29:23,670 --> 00:29:24,380
Everyone, gather up!

582
00:29:27,740 --> 00:29:28,590
Make way!

583
00:29:30,910 --> 00:29:31,740
Step aside!

584
00:29:31,740 --> 00:29:32,830
[Hats and Boots, Trustworthy Service]
Office of Justice on a case!

585
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:36,430
Sir,

586
00:29:36,430 --> 00:29:37,430
I need dry clothes.

587
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:39,950
Young man,

588
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:41,500
what happened to you?

589
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:43,950
I got pushed into the river while watching the commotion.

590
00:29:44,220 --> 00:29:45,140
What a coincidence.

591
00:29:45,620 --> 00:29:47,620
Just earlier, someone else came in soaked

592
00:29:47,620 --> 00:29:48,860
and asked for dry clothes.

593
00:29:49,190 --> 00:29:50,860
She said she got pushed into the river, too.

594
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,260
Sorry for troubling you.

595
00:31:22,670 --> 00:31:23,380
Wen Yue,

596
00:31:24,500 --> 00:31:26,740
I want to formally apologize to you on behalf

597
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:28,670
of Mo and Ban.

598
00:31:36,710 --> 00:31:37,910
This is between the two of us.

599
00:31:37,910 --> 00:31:39,620
What does it have to do with them?

600
00:31:43,070 --> 00:31:43,860
Zhao Buyou,

601
00:31:45,830 --> 00:31:47,070
I don't blame you

602
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,190
for keeping this from me.

603
00:31:50,910 --> 00:31:51,790
I know

604
00:31:52,620 --> 00:31:54,380
you were just trying to protect our family.

605
00:31:58,140 --> 00:31:59,460
But at the same time,

606
00:31:59,860 --> 00:32:00,830
I do hold it against you.

607
00:32:02,950 --> 00:32:04,100
You didn't trust me.

608
00:32:06,190 --> 00:32:07,710
You underestimated how much I valued

609
00:32:07,710 --> 00:32:09,980
the Zhao family living in Sparrow Lane.

610
00:32:20,710 --> 00:32:22,140
Even though I know the truth now,

611
00:32:23,430 --> 00:32:25,100
I still feel the same way.

612
00:32:29,550 --> 00:32:30,910
I still want us to stay together

613
00:32:33,140 --> 00:32:34,310
as a family.

614
00:32:42,140 --> 00:32:43,790
Let's go check on Ban.

615
00:32:44,710 --> 00:32:45,790
Come with me to visit her.

616
00:33:00,710 --> 00:33:01,500
Ban!

617
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:03,980
I've asked around.

618
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,620
The Luan couple

619
00:33:07,950 --> 00:33:09,460
died in prison from an illness outbreak.

620
00:33:09,590 --> 00:33:11,100
Died in prison from an illness outbreak?

621
00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:13,140
The information is reliable.

622
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:14,550
I just heard about it.

623
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:17,830
How could they

624
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:19,550
suddenly die like that?

625
00:33:20,790 --> 00:33:22,550
What did the coroner say after the examination?

626
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:23,950
Go ask again.

627
00:33:24,030 --> 00:33:25,380
I can't get anything more out of them.

628
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:26,460
You know their mouths

629
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:27,550
are sealed.

630
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:33,500
So Zou Mian wasn't trying to save them.

631
00:33:33,830 --> 00:33:35,430
He got them out to kill them.

632
00:33:36,070 --> 00:33:38,100
He'd even kill his own daughter and son-in-law.

633
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:39,590
How ruthless.

634
00:33:50,310 --> 00:33:51,340
I'll get the door.

635
00:33:55,070 --> 00:33:55,500
Bu...

636
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:57,590
Mr. Zhao.

637
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:02,710
Wen Yue and I were nearby,

638
00:34:03,310 --> 00:34:05,260
so we thought we'd stop by to check on you. Busy?

639
00:34:06,670 --> 00:34:07,460
Ban,

640
00:34:07,950 --> 00:34:10,110
have you not been eating properly?

641
00:34:10,460 --> 00:34:12,420
Look at you. You've lost weight.

642
00:34:13,390 --> 00:34:15,700
Right? I noticed it, too.

643
00:34:16,460 --> 00:34:17,460
Ban,

644
00:34:17,460 --> 00:34:18,390
come home.

645
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:20,500
You know how good my cooking is.

646
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,980
I... I forgot something outside.

647
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,390
Let them talk.

648
00:34:32,790 --> 00:34:34,460
Please take good care of her

649
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:36,150
while she's staying here.

650
00:34:37,180 --> 00:34:37,980
I will, Buyou.

651
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:52,700
Ban,

652
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:54,660
look at me.

653
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:58,390
I can't face you.

654
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:00,350
Listen,

655
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:02,870
the grudges of the previous generation

656
00:35:02,870 --> 00:35:04,500
are not yours to bear.

657
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:07,460
I'm sorry.

658
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,030
You've done nothing wrong.

659
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,870
Why are you apologizing to me?

660
00:35:15,980 --> 00:35:16,790
Wen Yue.

661
00:35:21,590 --> 00:35:23,630
Do you really still see me as family?

662
00:35:25,310 --> 00:35:26,790
What are you talking about?

663
00:35:29,870 --> 00:35:31,870
You were just this tall

664
00:35:32,110 --> 00:35:33,870
when I started living with you.

665
00:35:33,900 --> 00:35:35,460
Didn't I watch you grow up?

666
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:37,700
Of course, I see you as family.

667
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:45,150
What about Mo?

668
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:48,390
Mo did nothing wrong either.

669
00:35:50,420 --> 00:35:51,630
And Buyou?

670
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:54,420
Do you still blame him for hiding the truth from you?

671
00:35:58,070 --> 00:35:59,310
Of course, I understand

672
00:35:59,660 --> 00:36:01,500
why he did what he did.

673
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:04,180
He just wanted to protect

674
00:36:04,180 --> 00:36:05,700
the family we have now.

675
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:09,660
I don't blame him.

676
00:36:10,350 --> 00:36:11,740
And neither should you.

677
00:36:11,740 --> 00:36:12,550
Do you hear me?

678
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:17,350
The ones who committed those evil deeds are the ones to blame.

679
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:20,500
This will all pass.

680
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:24,070
When it's over,

681
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:28,310
we'll go back to how things used to be,

682
00:36:29,070 --> 00:36:30,500
and we'll never be apart.

683
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:36,700
Wen Yue,

684
00:36:40,260 --> 00:36:42,900
there's something I've always wanted to tell you.

685
00:36:43,460 --> 00:36:44,030
Go on.

686
00:36:45,070 --> 00:36:46,310
I used to

687
00:36:47,550 --> 00:36:49,740
envy others for having a mother.

688
00:36:52,940 --> 00:36:54,900
But ever since you became part of our family,

689
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:58,310
I've never envied anyone again.

690
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:14,390
[Wen's Umbrella Shop]

691
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:15,070
Slow down.

692
00:37:16,780 --> 00:37:17,780
No need to come out and greet me.

693
00:37:18,020 --> 00:37:18,590
It's fine.

694
00:37:28,260 --> 00:37:29,110
Wen Yue,

695
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:29,940
I...

696
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:36,390
I don't deserve to call her that anymore.

697
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:41,150
Lady Wen,

698
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:46,500
I copied some valuable clues from old case files in the archives.

699
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,020
They might help...

700
00:37:51,830 --> 00:37:52,700
No, not "help."

701
00:38:01,350 --> 00:38:02,150
Sir,

702
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:03,870
another pot of wine.

703
00:38:07,910 --> 00:38:08,980
Sir?

704
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:44,260
Zheng?

705
00:38:47,190 --> 00:38:48,020
I'm sorry.

706
00:38:48,390 --> 00:38:48,940
I...

707
00:38:51,150 --> 00:38:51,700
Be careful.

708
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,460
Let's sit down and talk.

709
00:38:57,590 --> 00:38:58,190
Are you okay?

710
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:02,390
Why did you drink so much?

711
00:39:05,300 --> 00:39:06,740
Why are you here, too?

712
00:39:12,070 --> 00:39:13,700
I lived near Taihu Lake when I was little.

713
00:39:14,540 --> 00:39:15,830
Whenever I miss home,

714
00:39:16,780 --> 00:39:18,670
I'll come here,

715
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:22,300
order Taihu Lake White Fish,

716
00:39:22,830 --> 00:39:24,870
and have a couple of drinks alone.

717
00:39:32,110 --> 00:39:34,190
I was going to give this to Wen...

718
00:39:35,740 --> 00:39:36,540
I mean,

719
00:39:36,980 --> 00:39:38,740
I was going to give this

720
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:40,540
to your sister.

721
00:39:41,910 --> 00:39:42,700
Zheng,

722
00:39:43,150 --> 00:39:44,430
you take it.

723
00:40:11,430 --> 00:40:12,350
You must've spent a long time

724
00:40:14,830 --> 00:40:16,020
going through the case files.

725
00:40:21,350 --> 00:40:22,150
Zheng,

726
00:40:23,830 --> 00:40:25,150
I owe you an apology.

727
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:29,020
Ban and I both do.

728
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:34,670
You don't need to apologize.

729
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:36,740
The dead can't come back to life.

730
00:40:37,110 --> 00:40:38,020
Your apology

731
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:40,670
won't bring my parents back.

732
00:40:43,460 --> 00:40:44,300
Besides,

733
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:46,350
aren't you and I

734
00:40:47,020 --> 00:40:48,190
both victims here?

735
00:40:48,940 --> 00:40:51,190
Wasn't your family also destroyed by Zou Mian?

736
00:40:51,190 --> 00:40:52,500
I'm sorry your efforts were wasted.

737
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:55,190
I wanted to gather more evidence,

738
00:40:56,740 --> 00:40:57,980
but Zou Mian erased

739
00:40:58,670 --> 00:41:01,070
every trace over the years.

740
00:41:02,260 --> 00:41:04,670
I've failed to atone for my father's sins,

741
00:41:05,870 --> 00:41:07,390
and I don't dare to avenge my family either.

742
00:41:08,110 --> 00:41:09,590
What kind of man am I?

743
00:41:11,110 --> 00:41:11,700
Too bad

744
00:41:13,150 --> 00:41:15,070
we're just scholars.

745
00:41:15,830 --> 00:41:18,430
We know who's behind it all and where to find him,

746
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:22,780
but we're powerless to do anything.

747
00:41:23,430 --> 00:41:24,350
It's too late.

748
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:26,590
The law can't touch him anymore.

749
00:41:27,830 --> 00:41:28,300
No,

750
00:41:29,190 --> 00:41:29,980
it's not too late.

751
00:41:30,460 --> 00:41:31,630
Now is the perfect time.

752
00:41:32,630 --> 00:41:33,780
"Better to die with a voice

753
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:36,540
than to live in silence."

754
00:41:38,830 --> 00:41:39,980
"Better to die with a voice

755
00:41:41,260 --> 00:41:42,430
than to live in silence."

756
00:41:48,590 --> 00:41:50,190
Zheng, you've read this article

757
00:41:50,910 --> 00:41:51,910
by the Duke of Wenzheng, too?

758
00:41:52,300 --> 00:41:53,670
Qiyu said that to me

759
00:41:54,830 --> 00:41:56,220
back at the welfare center.

760
00:41:57,260 --> 00:41:58,430
"If we're not at the table,

761
00:41:58,830 --> 00:41:59,830
we're on the menu."

762
00:42:00,540 --> 00:42:02,430
That's just how things work.

763
00:42:03,460 --> 00:42:04,540
Even the law

764
00:42:05,390 --> 00:42:07,670
is written by those in power.

765
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:15,110
I grieve for Qiyu,

766
00:42:16,910 --> 00:42:18,780
but I also admire his courage.

767
00:42:19,150 --> 00:42:20,220
"When an ordinary man is enraged,

768
00:42:20,220 --> 00:42:21,700
his fury can spill blood far and wide."

769
00:42:22,070 --> 00:42:24,630
He truly died with a voice.

770
00:42:26,540 --> 00:42:27,190
Mo,

771
00:42:29,700 --> 00:42:31,190
you must also wish for a world

772
00:42:31,740 --> 00:42:32,630
with fewer

773
00:42:32,980 --> 00:42:33,670
unfortunate souls

774
00:42:34,150 --> 00:42:34,830
like us,

775
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,830
my sister,

776
00:42:38,630 --> 00:42:39,430
Bo, and Qiyu.

777
00:42:39,910 --> 00:42:40,590
I do.

778
00:42:42,390 --> 00:42:43,300
Of course, I do.

779
00:42:46,110 --> 00:42:47,070
I knew it.

780
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:48,780
Just like Qiyu, you're someone

781
00:42:48,980 --> 00:42:50,390
who cares deeply for the greater good.

782
00:42:50,630 --> 00:42:51,830
Actually, we still have a chance.

783
00:42:52,300 --> 00:42:52,940
We just need to...

784
00:42:54,110 --> 00:42:55,110
A chance?

785
00:42:56,460 --> 00:42:57,430
What chance?

