00:43:46,150 --> 00:43:47,110
Moreover,

809
00:43:47,590 --> 00:43:49,390
the four iconic Chinese cooking methods,

810
00:43:49,590 --> 00:43:51,190
pan-frying, stir-frying,

811
00:43:51,190 --> 00:43:52,700
boiling, and deep-frying,

812
00:43:53,110 --> 00:43:55,740
all became widely used during the Song dynasty.

813
00:43:56,390 --> 00:43:57,190
How about that?

814
00:43:57,390 --> 00:43:59,070
Don't these fun facts

815
00:43:59,220 --> 00:44:00,670
make the food culture of the Song dynasty

816
00:44:00,670 --> 00:44:02,300
even more fascinating?

